body:
When converting [NullableBooleanDCR.cs](https://github.com/PowerShell/psl-monad/blob/source-depot/monad/tests/monad/src/engine/core/NullableBooleanDCR.cs) BVT case in line 191, create a function as:
`function ParserTestFunction
        {
            param([bool]$First) $First
        }`

Run command "& ParserTestFunction -First", no exception send out. The expected result should throw a exception.
